Name: RAKETENWASCHMACHINE
About the game: Hey! Who forgot to turn off the washing machine? Now the world is constantly spinning, not stopping for a second. RAKETENWASCHMACHINE is an action-puzzle game set in a constantly spinning world. Dozens of completely messed up levels will melt your brain or drive you crazy. • Fast-paced action-puzzle gameplay. • Beautiful pixel art. • Stylish chiptune soundtrack. • 20 hardcore levels. Avoid the obstacles and get to the end of the level
